{'id': 176431094, 'user_id': 2150383668, 'title': '光伏玻璃双寡头之一福莱特', 'text': '<p><img class="ke_img" src="https://xqimg.imedao.com/178a7f1c751c5cc3fef7d052.png!custom660.jpg" ></p><p><img class="ke_img" src="https://xqimg.imedao.com/178a7f1c6a99ada3fef41655.png!custom660.jpg" ></p><p><b>光伏相关阅读：</b></p><p>《<a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU5NzY3NTQwMg==&amp;mid=2247488958&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7e5eb101ba0cf7134c49bc3a0e926135&amp;chksm=fe4e895bc939004dfda7ee14f66a071c3e82068895ee86c73bb3aa8b949f4161e91b6f28fcfc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" title="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU5NzY3NTQwMg==&amp;mid=2247488958&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7e5eb101ba0cf7134c49bc3a0e926135&amp;chksm=fe4e895bc939004dfda7ee14f66a071c3e82068895ee86c73bb3aa8b949f4161e91b6f28fcfc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank">光伏逆变器龙头阳光电源</a>》</p><p>《<a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDIwNTQ1OA==&amp;mid=2247483731&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=36ccc8cf7cc06f12057851f81a2d1f8e&amp;chksm=c2e475aef593fcb893cf3b15469cb5935108cbee3802c4dd4b32fcec7f8fb31be59ce035e6f0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" title="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDIwNTQ1OA==&amp;mid=2247483731&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=36ccc8cf7cc06f12057851f81a2d1f8e&amp;chksm=c2e475aef593fcb893cf3b15469cb5935108cbee3802c4dd4b32fcec7f8fb31be59ce035e6f0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank">光伏龙头隆基股份</a>》</p><p>《<a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDIwNTQ1OA==&amp;mid=2247483768&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b9238ef2b5c58d44c7e5ed9d5d1d27c9&amp;chksm=c2e47585f593fc93298ecd6aecabe919d2195c84fd889c593a49c7857ca19673021638d5e88c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" title="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDIwNTQ1OA==&amp;mid=2247483768&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b9238ef2b5c58d44c7e5ed9d5d1d27c9&amp;chksm=c2e47585f593fc93298ecd6aecabe919d2195c84fd889c593a49c7857ca19673021638d5e88c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank">硅料电池片双料龙头通威股份</a>》</p><p>《<a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDIwNTQ1OA==&amp;mid=2247483924&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0c71dd647b0ad59298b6c334a